{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"157ef10b17","title":"不能放弃对党内最大走资本主义道路当权派的斗争","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0854c4cb6e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"157ef10b17","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ba52d9351","type":"title","text":"不能放弃对党内最大走资本主义道路当权派的斗争","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"157ef10b17","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9f618346f","type":"paragraph","text":"我个人觉得目前存在这样一个苗头，就是放弃对敌人斗争，对最大的党内走资本主义道路当权派的斗争。上次在这儿座谈的时候，曾经提出这个问题，我也讲过应该上纲，这个纲针对党内最大的走资本主义道路当权派。现在这个矛盾不集中，很分散。这样就难批臭党内最大的走资本主义道路的当权派。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"157ef10b17","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":578,"end":578}}}},"__N_SSG":true}